  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
      • edu.ncsu.csc216.get_outdoors.ui.TableModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ActivityTableModel, ParkTableModel, TrailTableModel

    public abstract class TableModel
extends javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
    TableModel is a wrapper for the information in List that can be used by a JTable.
